MESSAGE.value: Some ui work for creating new servings.
Add files missed in last commit.
Creating new foods and servings works.
Swapped add and search buttons in main ActionBar.

Fix bugs with editing values for multiple servings
It seems that calling setOnFocusChangedListener was wreaking havoc with keyboards. I've changed the way things are done now, to eliminate that. It still has issues with updates, particularly interactions with hitting the "done" button.

Lint cleanup
Made a few changes to resolve some lint issues. Many more to go.
